mkdir acme-agent-harness
cd acme-agent-harness
python3 -m orgs_ai_harness setup https://github.com/acme
```

The wizard asks which repos to cover, whether to clone them, and whether to generate global org skills, project-specific skills, or both. It also offers approval, eval replay, cache refresh, export, and explain steps.

